WEBVTT

1
00:32:52.520 --> 00:32:53.550 
等一下
Give me a sec.

2
00:32:55.360 --> 00:32:56.580 
其实…
Look...

3
00:32:56.600 --> 00:33:00.510 
我妈想约你家人谈一下酒席
Mom wants to talk to your family about the banquet.

4
00:33:00.840 --> 00:33:03.630 
酒席？我们摆酒吗？
Banquet?! We're doing a banquet?

5
00:33:03.640 --> 00:33:04.310 
就是…
Well...

6
00:33:04.320 --> 00:33:07.110 
一开始是说吃饭
It was supposed to be a dinner.

7
00:33:07.120 --> 00:33:09.390 
之后就要派喜帖
Then mom wanted to send out invitations,

8
00:33:09.400 --> 00:33:11.230 
之后又说要换裙褂
then she went on about getting dresses,

9
00:33:11.240 --> 00:33:13.070 
之后又说要换衣服
then she started talking about changing outfits...

10
00:33:13.080 --> 00:33:14.750 
那就是摆酒
So now it's a banquet.

11
00:33:15.160 --> 00:33:17.270 
你跟你家人谈谈吧
You should talk to your family.

